{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It's time to go on an adventure! Embark aboard an airship to discover the secrets of the clouds and... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Who knows? How far can you go? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cloud Piercer is a steampunk survival game with simple and effective mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> You are a group of adventurers at the controls of a flying machine, your duty will be to maintain it and subsist by exploring your environment, braving its dangers and exploiting its resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Travel the sky, find resources, destroy enemies, pierce the clouds to reveal their mysteries and survive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight against multiple types of war machines. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face fortresses to collect resources that will allow you to continue your journey but also to defend yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find the Edens, flying paradises filled with supplies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover new flying machines but also devastating attacks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Survive and earn points to unlock better ships and special abilities.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304500/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734645220","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304500/page.bg.jpg?t=1734645220","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304500/ad6618b0c09d7b433b1cafacfd6ce32919161f33/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734645220","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304500/ad6618b0c09d7b433b1cafacfd6ce32919161f33/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734645220","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"descriptio